{"tid":641660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟背叛美國 與中國聯手向WTO抗議鋼鋁稅","createTime":"2018-04-25T07:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T13:32:31.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a8530758b145e8913b16f89dc0911500311146","tid":641660,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"中國在世界貿易組織（WTO）抗議美國提高鋼、鋁進口關稅，歐盟昨日要求加入此行列，盼獲得鋼鋁關稅永久豁免。然而歐盟起初擬定的策略是與白宮和解並打壓中國。<br />\n<br />\n美國基於「國家安全」理由，提高鋼鐵進口關稅25%、鋁進口關稅10%，而歐盟獲得截至5月1日的暫時豁免。加拿大、墨西哥、澳洲、阿根廷、巴西皆在此列，而南韓已獲得永久豁免。而印度、俄國、挪威、新加坡、瑞士、土耳其和委內瑞拉紛紛在昨日提出對美國鋼鋁稅的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\nWTO表示，歐盟昨日已經正式要求加入中國發起的抗議行動。歐盟表示，一旦5月1日豁免結束，將重挫其出口鋼鋁，而距白宮做出決定僅剩1個星期，他們必須考量實質利益。WTO對於此議題目前處理程序為訴訟前諮商，而香港、印度、俄國和泰國皆已發出請求，與中國一同加入此諮商程序。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟執行委員會表示，歐盟終究視WTO諮商程序為最適合解決紛爭的方法，並希望也能無條件獲得永久豁免。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2404689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2404689&d=mamiB8kKqeBR%2BeAuePE5xL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8ce27009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2404689&h=b5933ce2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2404689</a><br />\n<br />\n舊垃圾幾時解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153e437ddb14c3ec96a9809331b13270f61ef600","tid":641660,"uid":17510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},{"pid":"2b3ffc9ca25388d42b232c162b10b71218c0bacb","tid":641660,"uid":75782,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"美國冇曬朋友？ <br />\n歐盟真正垃圾"},{"pid":"fff42840ecafdb9e4253d45f965eb0abd5f501e5","tid":641660,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"153e437ddb14c3ec96a9809331b13270f61ef600","tid":641660,"uid":17510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"好似得德國有出口鋼材去美國, 而且量唔多, 家下德國用歐盟個牌頭去同美國佬頂, 咁法國一上位, 成個歐盟即散晒"},{"pid":"21e8ca04100827d3637d21dcb45b898b4513a657","tid":641660,"uid":57376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"歐盟一向牆頭草<br />\n睇清楚內容<br />\n佢怕豁免期過左要收稅<br />\n即係侵侵一話唔收佢稅又會企侵果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c412677f82fd03aa61dc701db97898c0dc6bd336","tid":641660,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"再嘈咪退出世貿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d43b6a93a4c76d51bca375d137801fd7e0fe23f","tid":641660,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21e8ca04100827d3637d21dcb45b898b4513a657","tid":641660,"uid":57376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"歐盟一向牆頭草<br />\n睇清楚內容<br />\n佢怕豁免期過左要收稅<br />\n即係侵侵一話唔收佢稅又會企侵果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"大量連登仔不嬲只睇標題唔睇內文，兼唔用腦分析"},{"pid":"4dd3ba78b5940f79d9eadd4971015f060cd778c7","tid":641660,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d43b6a93a4c76d51bca375d137801fd7e0fe23f","tid":641660,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21e8ca04100827d3637d21dcb45b898b4513a657","tid":641660,"uid":57376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"歐盟一向牆頭草<br />\n睇清楚內容<br />\n佢怕豁免期過左要收稅<br />\n即係侵侵一話唔收佢稅又會企侵果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"大量連登仔不嬲只睇標題唔睇